&lt;p&gt;As a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Digital Media Executive&lt;/strong&gt;, you will work in lockstep with our Digital Centre of Excellence to design, execute, and optimize high-impact, multi-channel digital media campaigns. This is a highly analytical, data-driven, and fast-paced role requiring a blend of creative problem-solving and rigorous financial discipline. You will be responsible for translating client business objectives into high-performing media strategies, managing budgets with precision, and maximizing ROI across all paid digital channels.&lt;/p&gt;
