&lt;p&gt;The Group Tax Manager is responsible for leading and managing the tax function across WPP Scangroup’s operations in Africa. This role ensures&amp;nbsp; tax compliance across jurisdictions, optimizing the group’s tax position, overseeing tax accounting processes, manages tax audits and risks, and is the primary tax point of contact for Africa to support the business within a broader multinational group structure .&lt;/p&gt;
