&lt;li&gt;Develop, manage, monitor, and execute a transparent SEO strategic plan aligned with company goals and metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate regular reports on key SEO metrics and provide actionable insights for continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
