&lt;p&gt;As a practitioner and leader within the team, the Social Media Manager is responsible for creating, curating, and managing content across various social media platforms. They will develop and execute social media strategies, monitor performance metrics, and engage with the online community to drive engagement and growth. This role also includes the direct supervision and mentorship of Social Media Executives.&lt;/p&gt;
